### 2. UI & Navigation ([includes/sidebar.php](file:///c:/xampp/htdocs/tourmanagement/includes/sidebar.php), [core/session.php](file:///c:/xampp/htdocs/tourmanagement/core/session.php))

#### `function buildMenu($pdo, $parentId = 0, $userRole, $currentUrl)`
- **Location**: [includes/sidebar.php](file:///c:/xampp/htdocs/tourmanagement/includes/sidebar.php)
- **Description**: Recursively generates a sidebar menu based on User Role and Page hierarchy.
- **Parameters**:
  - `$pdo`: Database connection instance.
  - `$parentId` (int): ID of the parent page (default 0 for root).
  - `$userRole` (string): The role of the logged-in user.
  - `$currentUrl` (string): Used to set the `active` class on the current menu item.
- **Features**: Supports nested dropdowns (treeview) and access control (via `role_access` table).

#### `function getRoleBadgeColor($roleName)`
- **Location**: [core/session.php](file:///c:/xampp/htdocs/tourmanagement/core/session.php)
- **Description**: Generates a consistent Bootstrap badge color class based on the role name.
- **Mechanism**: Uses `crc32` hashing to map role names to a fixed set of Bootstrap colors.
- **Returns**: String (e.g., `text-bg-primary`).

