## Technical Specifications
- **Database Architecture**: 
  - `users`: Core user data.
  - `destinations`: Tour details (including JSON fields for `itinerary` and `activities`).
  - `sys_pages`: Dynamic registry of system pages.
  - `sys_roles`: System-defined user roles.
  - `role_access`: Junction table mapping roles to pages.
  - `system_settings`: Key-value pairs for global configurations (Site name, logo).
- **Security**: 
  - Prepared statements (PDO) to prevent SQL Injection.
  - `password_hash` / `password_verify` for credential security.
  - Session-based authentication with "Gatekeeper" checks in [header.php](file:///c:/xampp/htdocs/tourmanagement/includes/header.php).
- **UI Architecture**: 
  - Dark/Light mode support (stored in `localStorage`).
  - Recursive Breadcrumb generation based on page parent-child hierarchy.
